  "slug": "blasting-clay-and-clay-balls",
  "title": "Smelt Clay & Terracota in Blast Furnaces",
  "description": "Blast Clay, Clay Balls and Stained Terracotta, fully configurable",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kJdiggR.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blasting-clay-and-clay-balls\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/956343?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blasting-clay-and-clay-balls\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/blasting-clay-and-clay-balls?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This fully configurable mod allows you to smelt Clay, Clay Blocks, and Terracotta two times faster in the Blast Furnace than in the regular Furnace.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/haJFk6e.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"270\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i7ZQEF8.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"270\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rmPI78y.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"270\" /></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/blastingclay.json</code> in your profile folder. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>blasting_list</b> - A list of strings where each string represents a blasting recipe, specifying the input item, the output item, and the exp gained from blasting</p>\n</center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
